high_descs: Walk across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge, turn left and walk over to the wall then turn left again and walk up to the black table.
Pick up the head of lettuce off of the black table.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn right and walk forward, turn left to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the head of lettuce inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge back up and remove the now chilled head of lettuce, then close the fridge.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the black table.
Put the chilled head of lettuce on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce on a black table.

high_descs: Move to the wall head, turn right, move to the right side of the round table, turn left to face the lettuce on the right side of the round table.
Pick up the lettuce on the table.
Turn around, bring the lettuce to the fridge on the right.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge.
Take the chilled lettuce back to the right side of the round table.
Put the lettuce on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put chilled lettuce on the round table.

high_descs: Walk forward till you get just before the table, turn right, walk forward to the fridge, turn left and walk to the wall, then turn left again to face the table.
Pick the lettuce up from the table
Turn around, walk forward a step, turn right, walk forward till you hit the counter, then turn left to face the fridge
Place the lettuce on the top shelf beside the tomatoes, wait a few seconds, then remove it.
Turn left, walk to the wall, turn left again to face the table.
Put the lettuce back where you got it from.
anns.task_desc: Chill and return the lettuce to the table.
